    <text x="80" y="106" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="14" font-weight="700">Senior-exit wave reported (CoinDesk)</text>
    <text x="80" y="126" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="12">Stańczak, Stark, Van Epps, Monnot, Beiko and others leave</text>
    <circle cx="60" cy="190" r="7" fill="#38bdf8"/>
    <text x="80" y="184" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13">June 23</text>
    <text x="80" y="206" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="14" font-weight="700">New org structure announced</text>
    <text x="80" y="226" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="12">20% (54) staff cut · 40% budget cut · shift to 5 clusters</text>
    <circle cx="60" cy="290" r="7" fill="#f87171"/>
    <text x="80" y="284" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13">July 9</text>
    <text x="80" y="306" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="14" font-weight="700">Protocol Support team dissolved</text>
    <text x="80" y="326" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="12">5-year-old ACD/Forkcast/fellowship coordination team ends</text>
    <rect x="30" y="358" width="640" height="102" rx="10" fill="#0e2a1e" stroke="#4ade80" stroke-width="1.2"/>
